      • getThings

        public Set<Thing> getThings()
        Provides a Live reference to the Set<Thing> being in this location at the represented time instant. As the reference is live and the underlying data-structure is not Thread-safe, synchronization and concurrent access issues might arise in multi-threaded environments.
        Returns:
        the set of thing being in this location at the represented time.
